supportDesc.extent: 248 leaves : 250 x 170 (120 x 90) mm, bound to 250 x 170 mm
supportDesc.foliation: Modern foliation added in pencil, upper left recto; catchwords every verso, lower left. Folio number 57 is skipped (f. 56, 58) and folio number 247 repeats (f. 247, 247[a]).

layoutDesc.layout: 15 lines in two columns with 30 marginal lines in two sets of 15 across three sides.

scriptDesc.scriptNote: Naskh in black ink; pointed, vocalized.

history.provenance: Sequence of seals dated 125-/1834-45, 1252/1836-37, 1255/1839-40, and 1287/1870-71 (f. 157v). Customs stamp dated 1312/1894-95 (following 2r, 248v).
